# Library: github.com/muesli/reflow
#          ("reflow" — Christian Muehlhaeuser (muesli on GitHub)
#           — released 2020 as "Reflow lets you reformat blocks
#           of text in a terminal" for the Charm ecosystem.
#           Distinct from textwrap (Rust, R625), mitchellh/go-
